        <section class="yaqOZd" id="h.6526beaea2b0675d_20">
         <div class="IFuOkc">
         </div>
         <div class="mYVXT">
          <div class="LS81yb VICjCf j5pSsc db35Fc" tabindex="-1">
           <div class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-uQSCkd Ft7HRd-AhqUyc-uQSCkd purZT-AhqUyc-II5mzb ZcASvf-AhqUyc-II5mzb pSzOP-AhqUyc-qWD73c Ktthjf-AhqUyc-qWD73c JNdkSc SQVYQc">
            <div class="JNdkSc-SmKAyb LkDMRd">
             <div class="" jsaction="zXBUYb:zTPCnb;zQF9Uc:Qxe3nd;" jscontroller="sGwD4d" jsname="F57UId">
              <div class="oKdM2c ZZyype Kzv0Me">
               <div class="hJDwNd-AhqUyc-uQSCkd Ft7HRd-AhqUyc-uQSCkd jXK9ad D2fZ2 zu5uec OjCsFc dmUFtb wHaque g5GTcb" id="h.6526beaea2b0675d_17">
                <div class="jXK9ad-SmKAyb">
                 <div class="tyJCtd mGzaTb Depvyb baZpAe">
                  <div class="CobnVe yMxPgf aP9Z7e" id="h.ueid4tf0o868">
                  </div>
                  <h2 class="zfr3Q JYVBee CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" id="h.ueid4tf0o868_l" style="">
                   <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                    So what do you need?
                   </span>
                  </h2>
                  <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" style="">
                   <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                    Based on the 2024 checklist (which we were provided during admission), these are the requirements for you to have in-person.
                   </span>
                   <span class="C9DxTc" style="font-style: italic;">
                    All required documents should be original, with 2 photocopies for submission.
                   </span>
                  </p>
                  <ol class="n8H08c BKnRcf" style="list-style-type: decimal; margin-left: 0; margin-right: 0; padding: 0;">
                   <li class="zfr3Q TYR86d lsiHE" dir="ltr" style="margin-left: 15.0pt;">
                    <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="margin-left: 0.0pt; padding-left: 0.0pt; text-indent: 0.0pt;">
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial; font-weight: 700;">
                      Self-Attested copy of the ERP Profile
                     </span>
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                      : Once you have frozen your choice (or end of 6th round), you will get a mail giving access to ERP (See
                     </span>
                     <a class="XqQF9c" href="ERP%20-%20The%20College%20Portal.html" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none;">
                      <span class="C9DxTc aw5Odc" style="text-decoration: underline;">
                       ERP - The College Portal
                      </span>
                     </a>
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                     </span>
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                      for more info) in 2-3 days. Fill the required information, and once done, take a print-out of the ERP profile, and sign it.
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li class="zfr3Q TYR86d lsiHE" dir="ltr" style="margin-left: 15.0pt;">
                    <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="margin-left: 0.0pt; padding-left: 0.0pt; text-indent: 0.0pt;">
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial; font-weight: 700;">
                      Final Course Allotment Letter from JoSAA 2025
                     </span>
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                      : Available after freezing/6th round and paying the seet acceptance fee.
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li class="zfr3Q TYR86d lsiHE" dir="ltr" style="margin-left: 15.0pt;">
                    <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="margin-left: 0.0pt; padding-left: 0.0pt; text-indent: 0.0pt;">
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial; font-weight: 700;">
                      Admit Card of JEE (Advanced) 2025.
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li class="zfr3Q TYR86d lsiHE" dir="ltr" style="margin-left: 15.0pt;">
                    <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="margin-left: 0.0pt; padding-left: 0.0pt; text-indent: 0.0pt;">
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial; font-weight: 700;">
                      Undertaking Form
                     </span>
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                      - Original, and signed by both guardian &amp; student. Annex-3 of
                     </span>
                     <a class="XqQF9c" href="https://erp.iitkgp.ac.in/IITKGPApplications/admfile/PMRF.pdf" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">
                      <span class="C9DxTc aw5Odc" style="text-decoration: underline;">
                       Undertaking Docs
                      </span>
                     </a>
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                      .
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li class="zfr3Q TYR86d lsiHE" dir="ltr" style="margin-left: 15.0pt;">
                    <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="margin-left: 0.0pt; padding-left: 0.0pt; text-indent: 0.0pt;">
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial; font-weight: 700;">
                      Medical Certificate
                     </span>
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                      :
                     </span>
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                      Preferably KGP style.
                     </span>
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="font-variant: normal;">
                      Annex-
                     </span>
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                      1
                     </span>
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="font-variant: normal;">
                      of
                     </span>
                     <a class="XqQF9c" href="https://erp.iitkgp.ac.in/IITKGPApplications/admfile/PMRF.pdf" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">
                      <span class="C9DxTc aw5Odc" style="font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline;">
                       Undertaking Docs
                      </span>
                     </a>
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                      . (Some people used their JoSAA style last year without issues, but we haven't been able to verify if it wil work out this time.
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li class="zfr3Q TYR86d lsiHE" dir="ltr" style="margin-left: 15.0pt;">
                    <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="margin-left: 0.0pt; padding-left: 0.0pt; text-indent: 0.0pt;">
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial; font-weight: 700;">
                      Class X marksheet OR Birth Certificate
                     </span>
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                      : For proof of Date of Birth.
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li class="zfr3Q TYR86d lsiHE" dir="ltr" style="margin-left: 15.0pt;">
                    <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="margin-left: 0.0pt; padding-left: 0.0pt; text-indent: 0.0pt;">
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial; font-weight: 700;">
                      MarkSheet &amp; Certificate of passing qualifying
                     </span>
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                      (12th exam) : Both are the same for CBSE (Marksheet cum Certificate).
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li class="zfr3Q TYR86d lsiHE" dir="ltr" style="margin-left: 15.0pt;">
                    <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="margin-left: 0.0pt; padding-left: 0.0pt; text-indent: 0.0pt;">
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial; font-weight: 700;">
                      Aadhar Card.
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li class="zfr3Q TYR86d lsiHE" dir="ltr" style="margin-left: 15.0pt;">
                    <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="margin-left: 0.0pt; padding-left: 0.0pt; text-indent: 0.0pt;">
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial; font-weight: 700;">
                      3 Passport Photos (just in case).
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li class="zfr3Q TYR86d lsiHE" dir="ltr" style="margin-left: 15.0pt;">
                    <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="margin-left: 0.0pt; padding-left: 0.0pt; text-indent: 0.0pt;">
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial; font-weight: 700;">
                      Fees Acknowledgment.
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li class="zfr3Q TYR86d lsiHE" dir="ltr" style="margin-left: 15.0pt;">
                    <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="margin-left: 0.0pt; padding-left: 0.0pt; text-indent: 0.0pt;">
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial; font-weight: 700;">
                      Migrations Certificate &amp; Transfer Certificate if applicable :
                     </span>
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                      (Usually only for state boards &amp; stuff, but regardless try and get to be safe).
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li class="zfr3Q TYR86d lsiHE" dir="ltr" style="margin-left: 15.0pt;">
                    <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="margin-left: 0.0pt; padding-left: 0.0pt; text-indent: 0.0pt;">
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                      Caste/Category Certificate if applicable (includes EWS).
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li class="zfr3Q TYR86d lsiHE" dir="ltr" style="margin-left: 15.0pt;">
                    <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="margin-left: 0.0pt; padding-left: 0.0pt; text-indent: 0.0pt;">
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                      PwD certificate if applicable.
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li class="zfr3Q TYR86d lsiHE" dir="ltr" style="margin-left: 15.0pt;">
                    <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="margin-left: 0.0pt; padding-left: 0.0pt; text-indent: 0.0pt;">
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                      Passport/OCI/POI ID if applicable
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                   <li class="zfr3Q TYR86d lsiHE" dir="ltr" style="margin-left: 15.0pt;">
                    <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" role="presentation" style="margin-left: 0.0pt; padding-left: 0.0pt; text-indent: 0.0pt;">
                     <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                      Defence Certificate if applicable.
                     </span>
                    </p>
                   </li>
                  </ol>
                  <br/>
                  <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" style="">
                   <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                    Additionally, you might have to submit the migration certificate online too.
                   </span>
                  </p>
                  <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" style="">
                   <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                    Also, the extra forms you will have to fill out (if applicable) for IITKGP are available here :
                   </span>
                   <a class="XqQF9c" href="https://erp.iitkgp.ac.in/IITKGPApplications/admfile/PMRF.pdf" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">
                    <span class="C9DxTc aw5Odc" style="font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline;">
                     Undertaking Docs
                    </span>
                   </a>
                  </p>
                 </div>
                </div>
               </div>
              </div>
             </div>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
         </div>
        </section>
