                <div class="jXK9ad-SmKAyb">
                 <div class="tyJCtd mGzaTb Depvyb baZpAe">
                  <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" style="">
                   <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                    Basically the receipt of the Fees paid by you. Typically it will be the full fees, but the JoSAA Seat Acceptance Fees Receipt is also fine.
                   </span>
                  </p>
                  <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" style="">
                   <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                    This hasn't been verified with admin yet (10th July 2025), but given that many people will avail loans after coming to campus, I don't think so it's a requirement for you to have the full fees receipt =&gt; Hence why
                   </span>
                   <span class="C9DxTc" style="font-variant: normal;">
                    JoSAA Seat Acceptance Fees Receipt is also fine.
                   </span>
                  </p>
