                   <span class="C9DxTc" style="font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial; font-weight: 700;">
                    , we would recommend you to get one more medical certificate in the format given by IITKGP,
                   </span>
                   <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                    since that would ensure no issues at all.
                   </span>
                  </p>
                  <p class="zfr3Q CDt4Ke" dir="ltr" style="">
                   <span class="C9DxTc" style="">
                    That being said, some people did manage with the JoSAA format alone last year, and I don't think the IITKGP admin will be extremely strict in regards to this, but please try to get IITKGP style, until we confirm no issues.
